data.description: Welcome to 6440 W Gun Fury Rd in Eloy, Arizona! This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom horse property is now for sale! Sitting on about 1 acre of land. Walk inside and fall in love with the tile wood flooring and vaulted ceilings in the family room. The kitchen / dining area is open and spacious and perfect for entertaining. Notice the farmhouse sink where you can look out into your backyard and the mountain views. The master bedroom has an ensuite bathroom + walk in closet. 2 additional spacious bedroom. Indoor laundry room. Covered patio. Newer exterior & interior paint. Low-e tinted windows. Water heater less than a year old, new pump for the hauled water!
